attachments.title: Nokia reportedly shopping its HERE Maps division to Apple, others
attachments.text: Nokia is reportedly shopping its maps division to Apple, among other tech companies. According to a new report, Apple is one among many companies, including Amazon and Alibaba, that Nokia is targeting for a potential sale of its HERE Maps division.
